Package io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.dependency

Dependency management classes relating to installation, relocation, and loading into the global classpath can be found here.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArtifactManager
    This is the new improved dependency management class, which handles the dependencies of the project by managing them.
    EnhancedDependencyLoader
    Enhanced dependency loader which supports Java 16 and future Java versions.
    MMLDependencyInjector
    Injection class which utilizes SlimJar classes to load an ultimately append to the classpath while still supporting futuristic Java versions.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DependencyResolution
    A dependency resolution used for handling the types of dependencies MinecraftMediaLibrary uses.
    JarRelocationConvention
    A special class used to relocate the dependencies of MinecraftMediaLibrary.
    RepositoryDependency
    This is an enum used to store the dependencies MinecraftMediaLibrary will use during the runtime.
